    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《扫雷冒险谭2 ~露露姆的冒险~》是由知名独立游戏社团CelLab（セルレ部）制作，OTAKU Plan汉化发行的一款RPG游戏。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>★★注意事项★★</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分系统下，输入法会与游戏热键冲突，建议游戏前按下【Caps Lock】键开启大写模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏剧情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为某个事件，诺鲁鲁村的人们在回乡之际，归途上竟然布满了地雷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了带领大家安全地回到村子，机器人露露姆开始了扫雷的冒险历程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作品在扫雷游戏的基础上追加了多种新的游戏要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地面上表示的数字即周围埋藏的地雷个数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过这些数字来推测地雷的位置，并予以标记。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除此之外，扫雷过程中还会有多种协助或者阻扰判断的道具和陷阱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准确标记场上所有地雷即成功过关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多达上百关的扫雷体验并可随时切换游戏难度</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549240/extras/bedd4f0cd51bfb5a3664bd2c268b9274.avif?t=1770345373\" width=600 height=341 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>大地图左侧边栏随时确认操作指引</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549240/extras/2be80c40700acd4ee7c39a96b55a6137.avif?t=1770345373\" width=600 height=341 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装备技能让冒险更容易</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549240/extras/7917ec0bb52de1c008259acc797bf8da.avif?t=1770345373\" width=600 height=341 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>使用关卡奖励的星星升级技能</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549240/extras/b99b467a20507a3f671de9ecdf581748.avif?t=1770345373\" width=600 height=341 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>通关后可使用过关奖励解锁额外玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1549240/extras/e139767d0b62c75047878f9a39932cd3.avif?t=1770345373\" width=600 height=341 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Q&amp;A</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Q：大地图左侧边栏如何使用</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A：按下【X】键呼出左侧边栏，使用键盘的上下方向键切换功能，按【ESC】即可回到大地图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Q：额外关卡【无限塔】在哪？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A：使用关卡奖励的星星激活无限塔之后，无限塔将出现于第三章关卡的右侧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Q：【咖喱屋的挑战状】是什么？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A：使用关卡奖励的星星激活咖喱屋的挑战状之后，各关卡将追加第4项挑战内容，可以加速获得星星哦。</p>",
